title: Finally Apple Watch arrives in India on November 6
text:
Finally Apple Watch arrives in India on November 6 
merinews Friday 23rd October, 2015 
Apple has today updated its site to indicate that finally the Apple Watch will be available in India from November 6. Although prices of different variants have not been confirmed, but an update on it is expected soon. The estimated price of the Apple Watch Sport should be around INR 30,000.
